---
import { LuGlobe } from "react-icons/lu"
---

<section class="flex flex-col gap-y-6 print:gap-y-1" id="work">
  <div class="space-y-2">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold" id="work">Professional Experience</h2>
  </div><div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between"
      >
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold">Frontend Developer</h3><p
            class="text-sm text-muted-foreground"
          >
            Zventures LLC. · Full-Time
          </p>
        </div><div class="flex flex-col items-start text-sm md:items-end">
          <span class="inline-block rounded bg-secondary px-2 py-0.5 text-xs"
            >Narayanganj, Bangladesh</span
          ><span class="mt-1 text-muted-foreground">May 2024 – Present</span>
        </div>
      </div><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
        LinkBoss is an in-house internal linking platform developed by Zventures
        to simplify large-scale internal link management. It combines multiple
        specialized tools including inbound links, bulk operations, custom
        network builders, silo management, and reporting into a single
        application for efficient SEO workflows.
      </p><p
        class="mt-1 flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground"
      >
        <LuGlobe /><a href="https://zventures.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          >https://zventures.io</a
        >
      </p>
    </div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between"
      >
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold">Frontend Developer</h3><p
            class="text-sm text-muted-foreground"
          >
            GoGoshopBD · Contractual
          </p>
        </div><div class="flex flex-col items-start text-sm md:items-end">
          <span class="inline-block rounded bg-secondary px-2 py-0.5 text-xs"
            >Dhaka, Bangladesh</span
          ><span class="mt-1 text-muted-foreground">Apr 2023 – Dec 2023</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
        Contributed to the planning and development of a production e-commerce
        platform that shifted business operations from Facebook-based selling to
        a dedicated web application. Developed customer-facing features
        alongside an administrative portal for managing orders, inventory, and
        sales.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
